snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's VR: Help Wanted | Launch Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description: Five Nights at Freddy’s VR: Help Wanted is a collection of classic and original mini-games set in the five nights universe. Survive terrifying encounters with your favorite killer animatronics in a collection of new and classic Five Nights at Freddy experiences. “Where fantasy and fun come to life!”
